If rebuilding from scratch
1. Use the root-level files first.
2. Keep the 100-headline guarantee logic intact.
3. Preserve the globe widget and the write-up modal.
4. Keep the green CRT aesthetic subtle and readable.
5. Make sure mobile hides the globe entirely.
6. Re-run syntax checks before packaging.
